title: Our Church
lyrics:
This is our church
This is our church
This is our church
To every owner of an orange heart
Know that nothing shall tear it apart

When the world will try to divide us

Then this music will reunite us



May the heavens be praised with our sound

As we gather on holy ground

Where the doors are open wide

For the ones that have seen the light



This is our church

This is our church



Midnight wanderers

You are no longer alone

You have found a home

Let that light shine



This is our church
